Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_dptxfsiz#

Device Periodic Transmit FIFO-n Size Register (DPTXFSIZ)

This register holds the memory start address of each periodic TxFIFO to implemented in Device mode. Each periodic FIFO holds the data for one periodic IN endpoint. This register is repeated for each periodic FIFO instantiated.
